snippet.title: Amber Heard took picture of Johnny Depp passed out with tub of melted ice cream in his lap 'to show
snippet.description:
Amber Heard took picture of Johnny Depp passed out with a tub of melted ice cream in his lap 'to show how embarrassing and pathetic he was' - as court hears SHE was arrested for domestic violence in 2009 after screaming row with her then-girlfriend
#Amber @JohnnyDeoo
